thread.title_full: Public Storage reviewed by Amanda Barry

author: Amanda Barry
title: Amanda Barry
text: Without asking, the property manager offered suggestions for making the unit more cost effective, and provided tips to help protect my things, as well as tips to make the move much easier. For the unit, they were the cheapest around. Plus, the whole property seemed clean, safe, and well-maintained.
